{"tid":1461415,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"伊利沙伯醫院急症室醫生指香港正步向人道災難","createTime":"2019-08-13T07:40:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T08:01:15.000Z","uid":184679,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d592adf809096f38b463833c7b62a3d43e2f26d9","tid":1461415,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:40:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/files/images/20190813140602_190813144722_m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Ffiles%2Fimages%2F20190813140602_190813144722_m.jpg&h=66addf90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多間公立醫院在中午開始有醫護人員靜坐, 抗議警方濫用暴力. 其中在伊利沙伯醫院, 約200名戴上黑色口罩及黑絲帶的醫護人員, 在醫院主座大樓的樓梯靜坐.<br />\n<br />\n        他們手持印有「香港警察意圖謀殺香港市民」的示威語句, 並高叫口號. 部分人在右眼蓋上紗布, 以示抗議警方在周日的示威中, 懷疑用布袋彈擊中一名少女的眼睛.<br />\n<br />\n        發起集會的急症室醫生指, 連日來有多人因為警方的行動而受傷, 傷勢愈來愈嚴重, 認為香港正步向人道災難.<br />\n<br />\n        他又相信, 不少受傷示威者因擔心有被捕的風險, 不敢到醫院求診, 要求醫管局和食物及衛生局正視, 令市民重拾對公營醫療體系的信心.<br />\n<br />\n        有參與集會的護士批評, 醫護人員不斷救人, 但警方及政府不停傷害市民, 製造無辜的傷者, 令人心痛.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsId=20190813140602\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Flive.aspx%3FNewsId%3D20190813140602&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDb66fvQnHzZYMiebojCBKDlo%3D&h=4ef5946f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/live.aspx?NewsId=20190813140602</a>"},{"pid":"e7bf3d47f080b1b3efb70dc58f3a319b64f3f880","tid":1461415,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:52:23.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59d2ca782adc79d30891d6b59a4a960558706806","tid":1461415,"uid":2248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:01:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets